---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="サビイロネコ保護プロジェクト | SCIDI" 
  description="サビイロネコ保護プロジェクト - 密猟ゼロの世界へ。正規の「正門」を創る。SCIDI（希少種保全・疾病対策支援機構）"
>
  
    <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 bg-white shadow-md z-50 transition-all duration-300 mt-1" id="navbar">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                    <img src="https://page.gensparksite.com/v1/base64_upload/4e26ab94932310ed617b23c06f28d7db" alt="SCIDI Logo" class="h-12 w-12">
                    <div>
                        <div class="text-lg font-bold text-scidi-blue">SCIDI</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-gray-600">希少種保全・疾病対策支援機構</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-6">
                    <a href="#about" class="nav-link text-gray-700 hover:text-scidi-blue transition-colors py-2 border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-scidi-green">プロジェクトについて</a>
                    <a href="#crisis" class="nav-link text-gray-700 hover:text-scidi-blue transition-colors py-2 border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-scidi-green">危機の現状</a>
                    <a href="#solution" class="nav-link text-gray-700 hover:text-scidi-blue transition-colors py-2 border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-scidi-green">私たちの取り組み</a>
                    <a href="#roadmap" class="nav-link text-gray-700 hover:text-scidi-blue transition-colors py-2 border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-scidi-green">ロードマップ</a>
                    <a href="#team" class="nav-link text-gray-700 hover:text-scidi-blue transition-colors py-2 border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-scidi-green">チーム</a>
                    <a href="#partners" class="nav-link text-gray-700 hover:text-scidi-blue transition-colors py-2 border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-scidi-green">パートナー</a>
                    <a href="#support" class="bg-scidi-green text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-scidi-dark-green transition-all font-medium shadow-md hover:shadow-lg">支援方法</a>
                </div>
                
                <button class="md:hidden text-scidi-blue" id="mobile-menu-button">
                    <i class="fas fa-bars text-2xl"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="hidden md:hidden pb-4" id="mobile-menu">
                <a href="#about" class="block py-2 text-gray-700 hover:text-scidi-blue transition-colors border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-scidi-green pl-4">プロジェクトについて</a>
                <a href="#crisis" class="block py-2 text-gray-700 hover:text-scidi-blue transition-colors border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-scidi-green pl-4">危機の現状</a>
                <a href="#solution" class="block py-2 text-gray-700 hover:text-scidi-blue transition-colors border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-scidi-green pl-4">私たちの取り組み</a>
                <a href="#roadmap" class="block py-2 text-gray-700 hover:text-scidi-blue transition-colors border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-scidi-green pl-4">ロードマップ</a>
                <a href="#team" class="block py-2 text-gray-700 hover:text-scidi-blue transition-colors border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-scidi-green pl-4">チーム</a>
                <a href="#partners" class="block py-2 text-gray-700 hover:text-scidi-blue transition-colors border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-scidi-green pl-4">パートナー</a>
                <a href="#support" class="block py-2 mt-2 bg-scidi-green text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-scidi-dark-green transition-all text-center font-medium">支援方法</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden" id="hero">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('https://page.gensparksite.com/v1/base64_upload/1324d3d31cd6e631a40b337144f3493a'); filter: brightness(0.6);"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/40 to-black/60"></div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 text-center text-white px-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-16 sm:mt-0">
            <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight animate-fade-in-up">
                密猟ゼロの世界へ。<br>
                正規の「正門」を創る
            </h1>
            <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl mb-8 font-medium animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-200">
                世界最小級の野生ネコ、サビイロネコを守る
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-400">
                <a href="#about" class="bg-scidi-green text-white px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 sm:py-4 rounded-full text-base sm:text-lg font-bold hover:bg-scidi-dark-green transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
                    詳しく知る
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-white text-3xl"></i>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-white" id="about">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-scidi-blue mb-4">サビイロネコとは</h2>
                <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-scidi-green mx-auto"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">世界最小級の野生ネコ科動物</h3>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                            <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt text-scidi-green text-2xl mt-1"></i>
                            <div>
                                <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">生息地</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">スリランカ・インド固有種</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                            <i class="fas fa-weight text-scidi-green text-2xl mt-1"></i>
                            <div>
                                <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">体重</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">0.9-1.6kg（成体）</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle text-red-500 text-2xl mt-1"></i>
                            <div>
                                <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">絶滅危機レベル</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">IUCN準絶滅危惧種（VU: Vulnerable）</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">ワシントン条約（CITES）附属書Ⅱ類</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bg-scidi-light-blue p-6 rounded-lg">
                        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
                            <span class="font-bold text-scidi-blue">家猫の約1/3〜1/4の大きさ</span>という世界最小級の野生ネコ科動物です。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-8">
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-8">大きさ比較</h4>
                        <div class="space-y-8">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                                <div class="text-center flex-1">
                                    <i class="fas fa-cat text-gray-600 text-6xl mb-3"></i>
                                    <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">一般的な家猫</p>
                                    <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-scidi-blue">3.5-4.5kg</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-4xl text-gray-400 px-4">VS</div>
                                <div class="text-center flex-1">
                                    <i class="fas fa-cat text-scidi-green text-4xl mb-3"></i>
                                    <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">サビイロネコ</p>
                                    <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-scidi-green">0.9-1.6kg</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-20">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-12">主な脅威</h3>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                    <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 text-center hover:border-scidi-green transition-all hover:shadow-lg">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-secret text-red-500 text-3xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">密猟・密輸</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">毛皮やペット目的の違法捕獲</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 text-center hover:border-scidi-green transition-all hover:shadow-lg">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-tree text-orange-500 text-3xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">生息地破壊</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">森林伐採による住処の消失</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 text-center hover:border-scidi-green transition-all hover:shadow-lg">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-dollar-sign text-purple-500 text-3xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">違法取引</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">高額で取引される希少動物</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50" id="crisis">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-scidi-blue mb-4">なぜ今、行動が必要か</h2>
                <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-scidi-green mx-auto"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-20">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-scidi-blue to-scidi-dark-green rounded-2xl p-12 text-white text-center shadow-2xl">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">世界の動物違法取引の経済規模</h3>
                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <p class="text-lg mb-4">年間の違法取引額（UNEP/INTERPOL推計）</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-4">
                            <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white/80">最大</p>
                            <div class="relative">
                                <p class="text-7xl md:text-9xl font-black">3.4</p>
                                <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-4 h-4 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full animate-ping"></div>
                                <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-4 h-4 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full"></div>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black">兆円</p>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 mb-2">（1兆円〜3.4兆円）</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="inline-block bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm px-8 py-4 rounded-full">
                        <p class="text-2xl font-bold">世界4位の国際組織犯罪</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg">
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                        この巨大な犯罪市場は、「可愛い、珍しい」といった私たちの純粋な興味や、「希少動物を所有したい」という歪んだ欲求を悪用し、
                        莫大な利益を上げ、その利益を<span class="font-bold text-red-600">犯罪や紛争に流出</span>させます。また、管理されていない動物の移動は、
                        将来パンデミックを起こしかねない<span class="font-bold text-red-600">未知の感染症（ズーノーシス）を拡散</span>させる、公衆衛生上の深刻なリスクを孕みます。
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-12">経済損失と影響の連鎖</h3>
                
                <div class="mb-16">
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-center text-scidi-blue mb-8">① 犯罪・紛争への影響</h4>
                    <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <div class="w-28 h-28 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 shadow-lg">
                                <i class="fas fa-user-secret text-white text-3xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">密猟</p>
                        </div>
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-gray-400 text-3xl"></i>
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <div class="w-28 h-28 bg-gray-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 shadow-lg">
                                <i class="fas fa-mask text-white text-3xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">犯罪組織の<br>資金源</p>
                        </div>
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-gray-400 text-3xl"></i>
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <div class="w-28 h-28 bg-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 shadow-lg">
                                <i class="fas fa-bomb text-white text-3xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">テロ・<br>地域紛争</p>
                        </div>
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-gray-400 text-3xl"></i>
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <div class="w-28 h-28 bg-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 shadow-lg">
                                <i class="fas fa-leaf text-white text-3xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">生態系破壊</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="md:hidden space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg mb-2">
                                <i class="fas fa-user-secret text-white text-2xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm">密猟</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-arrow-down text-gray-400 text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gray-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg mb-2">
                                <i class="fas fa-mask text-white text-2xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm">犯罪組織の資金源</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-arrow-down text-gray-400 text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg mb-2">
                                <i class="fas fa-bomb text-white text-2xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm">テロ・地域紛争</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-arrow-down text-gray-400 text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg mb-2">
                                <i class="fas fa-leaf text-white text-2xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm">生態系破壊</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-center text-scidi-blue mb-8">② 感染症リスクへの影響</h4>
                    <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <div class="w-28 h-28 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 shadow-lg">
                                <i class="fas fa-user-secret text-white text-3xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">密猟</p>
                        </div>
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-gray-400 text-3xl"></i>
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <div class="w-28 h-28 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 shadow-lg">
                                <i class="fas fa-plane text-white text-3xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">管理不足の<br>国際輸送</p>
                        </div>
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-gray-400 text-3xl"></i>
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <div class="w-28 h-28 bg-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 shadow-lg">
                                <i class="fas fa-virus text-white text-3xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">パンデミック<br>リスク</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="md:hidden space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg mb-2">
                                <i class="fas fa-user-secret text-white text-2xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm">密猟</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-arrow-down text-gray-400 text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg mb-2">
                                <i class="fas fa-plane text-white text-2xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm">管理不足の国際輸送</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-arrow-down text-gray-400 text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg mb-2">
                                <i class="fas fa-virus text-white text-2xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm">パンデミックリスク</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-white" id="solution">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-scidi-blue mb-4">私たちのアプローチ：「正門」を創る</h2>
                <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-scidi-green mx-auto mb-6"></div>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    合法的かつ適正な利益となる正規ルートを確立し、密猟の根本原因に対処
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-8">対策アプローチの比較</h3>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-200 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-times text-white text-3xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">既存の対策：「裏口」を塞ぐ</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                            多くの団体が違法取引というルートを取り締まりますが、密猟の経済的動機に対処できていません
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-scidi-green rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-scidi-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-check text-white text-3xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">SCIDIのアプローチ：「正門」を創る</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                            合法的かつ適正な利益となる正規ルートを確立し、密猟の根本原因に対処
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-16">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-12">「正門」モデルの3本柱</h3>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-scidi-blue to-blue-700 rounded-xl p-8 text-white shadow-xl">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                            <span class="text-3xl font-bold">1</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">正規導入</h3>
                        <ul class="space-y-3 text-white/90">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-scidi-green mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                <span>CITES等の法令を完全遵守</span>
                            </li>
